---
title: LA Municipal.FYI
---

    <div class="jumbotron">
      <div class="container">

		<div class="row">
		  <div class="col-md-6">
			 <h1>LA Municipal.FYI</h1>
		<p>After an intense 2016 election, it seems people are more fired up about politics than ever before. Luckily for us Angelenos, there is another election around the corner. <b>March 7th</b> we head to the polls to pick our city leaders, and every vote counts in these historically low turnout elections. This is a small effort to raise awareness about what is at stake this spring, get out there and vote!</p>
		<p><a class="btn btn-primary btn-lg" href="http://lavote.net/home/voting-elections/current-elections/find-my-election-information?polling-location" role="button">Find Your District</a></p>
		  </div>
		  <div class="col-md-6">
			<h2>Races</h2>

			<% data.election.races.each do |r| %>
			<ul class="list-group">
				<li class="list-group-item tc"><%= r.title %> - <%= r.description %></li>

			</ul>


			<% end %>



			<h2>LA City and County Measures</h2>
			<% data.election.measures.each do |r| %>
			<ul class="list-group">
				<li class="list-group-item tc"><%= r.title %> - <%= r.description %></li>

			</ul>


			<% end %>




		  </div>
		</div>


      </div>
    </div>
	  
	<div class="container">
	  
		<div class="rowsOfItems">
		
			<% data.election.races.each do |r| %>
			
				<div style="width:100%">
					
					<div style="padding-top: 20px;">
						<h2><%= r.title %></h2>
						<% if r.measure===false %>
						<div class="row">
							<div class="description">
								<p><%= r.description %></p><strong>Candidates</strong>
							</div>		
							<div class="col-md-12">
								<% r.candidates.each do |c| %>
									<%= partial("candidate", :locals => { :name => c.name, :title => c.title, :website => c.website, :image => c.image, :incumbent => c.incumbent, :endorsed => c.endorsed} ) %>
								<% end %>
							</div>
						</div>
						<% else %>
						<div class="row">
							<div class="description">
								<p><%= r.description %></p><strong>Yes and No</strong>
							</div>
							<div class="col-md-12">
							
							</div>
						</div>
						<% end %>
					</div>
				
				</div> <! width 100% !> 
			
			<% end %><! do loop !>
		
		</div> <!colmd9!>
		
	</div>